dc_title_s: Chorographia Terrae Sanctae in angustiorem formam redacta
dc_description_s: Oriented with north to the lower left. Shows distribution of the tribes. Inset: oval map of ancient Jerusalem, "Hierosolymas veteris imago." Along sides and bottom: 16 vignettes of biblical objects. Plan of the Temple in the lower left corner and view of the Temple in the lower right corner. Printed on two sheets joined. 1 map; 33 x 85 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
